  "text": "The in vitro translation assays described in Table 1 (below) were performed in HeLa S3 cell extracts prepared by following a reported protocol [CITATION_1] . Briefly, 80 ng of capped dicistronic transcript was mixed with 4 µl of cell lysate in a final reaction volume of 10 µl containing 16 mM Hepes/KOH, pH 7.6, 20 mM creatine phosphate, 0.1 µg/µl creatine kinase, 0.1 mM spermidine, 100 µM amino acids, 50 mM potassium acetate and 2.5 mM magnesium acetate. The translation reactions were carried out at 37",
